1.0.name: wordpress/manycontacts-bar
1.0.description: The ManyContacts Bar for is a Free Contact Form WordPress plugin that make it really simple to copy and paste your ManyContacts Bar code snippet from manycontacts.com, straight to your WordPress admin interface. The Free Contact Form is optimized with honey-trap captcha, data incrementing and lead qualification.
